        </table>
        <p>Create an Account on <a target="_blank" href="https://www.maxmind.com/en/geoip2-services-and-databases">MaxMind</a> and generate a license key from <a target="_blank" href="https://www.maxmind.com/en/accounts/444238/license-key">here</a>.</p>
